HEADWORD: Estrapade
<hw>Es`tra*pade"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<fld>(Man.)</fld> <def>The action of a horse, when, to get rid of his
rider, he rears, plunges, and kicks furiously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

